{"tid":1309672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實唔比人拆得既連儂牆根本就唔係連儂牆 咪再咁執著","createTime":"2019-07-12T10:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T10:24:11.000Z","uid":9566,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9256299bb1c568cd8920b99979d2f1e0e509fab4","tid":1309672,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:07:57.000Z","msg":"連儂牆既精神就係 不怕暴政 <br />\n拆完再起 起完比人拆又再起 不停LOOP 話比人知我地既聲音係永遠不會被毀滅<br />\n如果你起完冇比人拆 一直留係到 根本唔係叫連儂牆 個意義係冇撚晒<br />\n所以我呼籲各位巴絲打 見到幅牆比人拆 唔洗太勞氣 影低班垃圾點樣破壞 放上網話比人知 有危險就走 唔洗動粗 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">然後重點係 比人拆完之後 一定要去起返 要同全世界講 拆一貼十 無論你拆幾多 我地都會企得返起身！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9b3cb4374cca0a761214fd414afe33ce14db4bd0","tid":1309672,"uid":9566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:10:38.000Z","msg":"BE WATER"},{"pid":"65c88ca6b511ee7f1bfac494e1b237c3e2325d07","tid":1309672,"uid":264811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4fdc0019da6bc7b19a440e55ef995a05ef54be","tid":1309672,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:14:45.000Z","msg":"要擁有 必先懂失去怎接受"},{"pid":"c3cc400c4821a015e579dce5d512b4d7bbe1aa77","tid":1309672,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad4fdc0019da6bc7b19a440e55ef995a05ef54be","tid":1309672,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:14:45.000Z","msg":"要擁有 必先懂失去怎接受"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:16:13.000Z","msg":"識野"},{"pid":"30ade41846567edfaca2bf13fce599c76c4cebb9","tid":1309672,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:19:46.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"2d37d94e2ee2d62684195a84fe3938868e5d28b0","tid":1309672,"uid":20362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:21:50.000Z","msg":"我真係唔明 個個當幅牆傳家之寶咁<img src